* Iriss' scanners pick up a new signature that had just arrived at the Ark 
(Quake), quickly scanning him over and storing his info into her personal 
data banks...since the Arks were scrap.
She watched him carefully through a half functioning moniter that had 
somehow missed most of the damage of the battles, repairing it as she 
watched.
There were no weapons which functioned on this ship so she was glad that he 
was a Maximal, watching him take out his gun.
The main circuits which lead to the consoles were completely severed, 
cutting off her chances of repairing them.
But she would get the chance to repair later, for now she thought it quite 
interesting to watch this bot standing in front of the base.*
